Our users can link their credit card and pick the portfolio of cryptocurrencies that they want to Our users can link their credit card and pick the portfolio of cryptocurrencies that they want to invest in. Additionally our users can convert their existing portfolio into a new one.

Body: I change this rule, not for my benefit, I changed it for the honest participants who work hard and deserve the rewards. I changed it because many spammers were joining the bounty those who don't even have Bitcointalk account they were also joining with the fake information. Our Social Media Campaign got more than 750 Participants in just 1 week and more than 50% of them are spammers with fake accounts and I don't want to give this rewards to the spammers. If you can work hard for posting and sharing you can also work a bit posting the proof here. This will eliminate the fake accounts factors because only those participants will be able to post proof here who have real bitcointalk account. If you think this is wrong that I am thinking about the honest workers then I can only say sorry for that but I hope you will understand what I am saying. And yes if I think changing the rules will benefit the honest participants I will and honest participants will also understand this. Sorry for the inconvenience you faced...

Author: shams
Title: [BOUNTY] üî•Coinseedüî•-Spare change investment and portfolio management
Body: Coinseed - Spare change investment and portfolio management Coinseed Bounty Program  ICO and Bounty Extended for One More Month till 20th May 2018 I will start to update the stakes in Social Media Bounty after 1st May 2018. And Blog & Media will be at the End.  Coinseed Micro-investment platform in cryptocurrency.  Coinseed automatically collects your spare change and invest it in your portfolio of cryptocurrencies. We gamified the creation of investment portfolios and our users can see how other users are doing it and can even copy the best performing portfolios. When a Coinseed user converts their current portfolio to another portfolio, there is a 1% fee on the total asset that is being converted. Coinseed will distribute 50% of this revenue to the CSD token holders every month. Our app is live in the US and we're planning to make a global release in February.  Website - WhitePaper - Facebook - Twitter - Telegram - Medium - Instagram - Linkedin  Presale ICO: 12/20/17‚Äì01/10/18  ICO: 03/20/18‚Äì05/20/18  5% of the Total Supply of 10 000 000 CSD are reserved for the Bounty Program   Coinseed Bounty Program includes the following campaigns: 1.   Social Media Campaign (Facebook, Twitter) 2.   Media / Blogging Campaign (Articles, Blog Posts, Videos on YouTube). 3.   Signature Campaign 4.   Translations of Whitepaper 5.   Membership Campaign  The 5% of all the tokens reserved for the bounty program will be distributed to all the campaigns: Social Media Campaign ‚Äî 20% Media / Blogging Campaign ‚Äî 30% Signature Campaign ‚Äî 35% Whitepaper Translation ‚Äî 10% Membership Campaign ‚Äî 5%  General Terms  We are going to assign ‚Äústakes‚Äù to bounty-hunters in certain amounts for performing specific actions within one or several of our bounty campaigns. The stakes will be proportionally distributed among the participants of the bounty program upon its closure in accordance with the number of stakes gathered by each participant.  We reserve the right to remove anyone of the participants from any campaign at any time if we think that they are not honest.  We reserve the right not to accept certain potential participants to the bounty program without having to explain why.  All the campaigns have specific rules. Please study those rules carefully.  For Facebook, Twitter campaigns the number of friends and/or followers is essential.  For Media / Blogging campaign in addition to the number of friends/ followers/subscribers the quality of the written / video content will be taken into consideration as well.  We reserve the right to change the general terms as well as the rules specific for each of the bounty campaigns during the bounty program upon our sole discretion and with the preliminary announcement for bounty-hunters via email and/or on our bitcointalk.org and medium profiles.  Social Media Campaign  JOIN HERE Spreadsheet  Facebook  300+ friends/followers ‚Äî 10 stakes 1000+ friends/followers ‚Äî 20 stakes 3000+ friends/followers ‚Äî 50 stakes  1 Post = 1 Stake (Max 3 Per Week) 1 Share = 1 Stake (Max 7 Per Week)  Rules: 1.   Follow us on Facebook and keep following us until the end of the bounty program. 2.   You need to have at least 300 real friends/followers. 3.   Your profile setting must be set to public. 4.   You have to like and Share all the Official Posts. 5.   You can share up to 7 posts per Week. Only Official post sharing will be counted. 6.   You can make 3 Posts per Week. In the posts use the hashtag #coinseed. 7.   1 Stake will be given for 1 post/Share. Max 7 Shares per week. Max 3 Post per Week. 8.   Sunday will be the last day of the week. Post/Shares on Monday will be counted in next week. 9.   You need to submit report weekly in the Bounty Thread with the entire Post/Shares links. I will explain the format below these Rules. 10.   If we find your Facebook account is only used for ICO and Crypto Sharing and No Personal Post You will be disqualified. 11.   Joining with Bot, Multiple, Inactive accounts is not allowed if we find someone doing this will be disqualified from the whole bounty campaign.
